{
  "stem": "4760.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in-- at-- she used to cook the brisket and on Pesach, we used to make the matzo ball soup.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to have chicken every Friday night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a-- a tradition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And-- and if you know a [? shallot? ?] You know what [? shallot ?] is?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's a potato kugel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She used to cook that every Friday night, so that was a tradition.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the family, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just read up on Laufersweiler the other day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first Jews moved into Laufersweiler in 1751.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in order to move into that town, they had to pay a tax in-- in those days, all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I grew up, we had about 25 Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were about 100 Jewish people living  in Laufersweiler.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Laufersweiler was a fairly large, large Jewish community because we were about the only big temple in its surrounding of 20, 30 miles.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other towns had very little shuls, just a little room to-- to go on Saturdays to make-- if they had enough people to make minyan.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But most of the time, Laufersweiler always had a minyan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- they used to go to Friday night service, Saturday night, and Saturday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We-- we observed all that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time, when-- when we lived in Laufersweiler, my mother was very well liked-- first because she lost her husband, and then the people would help her so that she could stay in business and support her family.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even the Gentiles, they would always shop by her and come to the-- to the [INAUDIBLE] have a glass of beer, or a schnapps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- the-- the Gentile families on our surrounding were very, very nice to-- to our family, to our family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anti-Semitism started in 1936-- in 1934, I mean.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
